MITCHELL, Respondent, v. ROCHESTER RY. CO., Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. March 27, 1894.) Action by Annie Mitchell against the Rochester Railway Company.

Argued before DWIGHT, P. J., and LEWIS, HAIGHT, and BRADLEY, JJ.

No opinion. Order granting new trial appealed from affirmed, with costs on opinion of Rumsey, J., at circuit 25 N. Y. Supp. 744.
